\b 1. Suite Overview\b0\par
Arcade Commander 2.0 ships as a 3-component Windows suite:\par
- ArcadeCommanderV2.exe (main UI)\par
- ACLighter.exe (background lighting service/tray app)\par
- ACDispatch.exe (dispatcher CLI for event automation)\par
