\b 2. Installation and Startup Order\b0\par
Recommended launch order:\par
1) Start ACLighter.exe\par
2) Start ArcadeCommanderV2.exe\par
3) Use ACDispatch.exe for automation/testing\par
\par
Runtime communication endpoint: 127.0.0.1:6006\par
