\b ARCADE COMMANDER\b0\par
Primary live control workspace. Includes the bottom utility bar controls:\par
APPLY, ALL OFF, BTN TEST, SWAP FIGHT, SWAP START, LED TEST, CYCLE, DEMO, PORT, ABOUT, HELP, QUIT\par
