\b 6. ACLighter Operations\b0\par
ACLighter listens on 127.0.0.1:6006 and accepts state/animation commands.\par
Tray menu options:\par
- STRESS: Plasma\par
- STRESS: Hyper Strobe\par
- Test: Rainbow\par
- Reset (Off)\par
- Exit\par
