\b 7. ACDispatch CLI Quick Reference\b0\par
\f1 ACDispatch.exe\f0  (send idle reset)\par
\f1 ACDispatch.exe --anim RAINBOW\f0  (trigger animation)\par
\f1 ACDispatch.exe --event GAME_START <rom_name>\f0  (trigger event mapping)\par
\f1 ACDispatch.exe <rom_name>\f0  (load game profile behavior)\par
\par
Supported event family:\par
FE_START, FE_QUIT, SCREENSAVER_START, SCREENSAVER_STOP, LIST_CHANGE, GAME_START, GAME_QUIT, GAME_PAUSE, AUDIO_ANIMATION, SPEAK_CONTROLS, DEFAULT\par
