\b 8. Troubleshooting\b0\par
\b No lighting response\b0\par
- Confirm ACLighter is running\par
- Confirm port 6006 is available\par
- Confirm correct PORT selection in Commander\par
- Use ALL OFF then APPLY to force state refresh\par
\par
\b Effect visible in FX Editor but missing elsewhere\b0\par
- Confirm save to shared library files in data\\library\par
- Reload selector/app and verify entry format\par
\par
\b Preview works but hardware does not\b0\par
- Confirm ACLighter listener active\par
- Validate physical hardware path\par
- Run LED TEST and BTN TEST\par
